{"tid":2355196,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"西洋畫 （風景畫）推薦？","createTime":"2021-01-06T03:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T05:09:45.000Z","uid":58963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c749458357e323b5649826da9609414187cfea","tid":2355196,"uid":58963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"偶爾機會之下見到呢幅畫，非常悠閒自然。<br />\n1565年，差唔多成四百幾年前既作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/05/Pieter_Bruegel_the_Elder-_The_Harvesters_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F05%2FPieter_Bruegel_the_Elder-_The_Harvesters_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg&h=c4e5d726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPieter Bruegel the Elder / 1565 / Oil on wood / 119 cm &times; 162 cm (​46 7&frasl;8 in &times; ​63 3&frasl;4 in)<br />\n<br />\n同一作者仲有另一幅：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/af/Die_Heuernte.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Faf%2FDie_Heuernte.jpg&h=f2d97f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身藝術既野，我識條鐵，<br />\n不過比較寫實既風景畫係吸引到我既興趣。<br />\n唔知大家有無一d自己覺得好靚既風景畫，<br />\n一齊share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca4cd16e5088c6866a3bac7e2990bd0d8abc029","tid":2355196,"uid":58963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"當代既畫都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce056612673ebdf038191344f69a80aca640b1d4","tid":2355196,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"少睇landscape<br />\n<br />\nanyway<br />\n<br />\n以前既西方畫都有個問題<br />\n就係太過公式化，數理化<br />\n好似Golden Ratio，三庭五眼<br />\n根本同靚字無咩關係<br />\n<br />\nGolden ratio黎到近代已經無人想聽咁滯<br />\n<br />\n講真啦<br />\nrenaissance artist 係無電腦既時代畫到咁係好勁<br />\n但係咪靚就見仁見智<br />\n現代畫家要比既，係無佢地咁專，咩都識咩都精咁<br />\n即係